			<title>Club Closed</title>
			<link>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/45-featured/1081-club-closed</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/45-featured/1081-club-closed</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div dir="ltr" style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;" data-setdir="false">In light of the latest advice from British Canoeing and the Environment Agency, we will have to abide by their guidance and cease all paddle sport activity until advised otherwise.</div>
<div dir="ltr" style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;" data-setdir="false">&nbsp;</div>
<div dir="ltr" style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;" data-setdir="false">I would advise anybody thinking of ignoring this directive to reconsider as doing so would bring the club into disrepute.&nbsp; I thank you for your cooperation in this matter.&nbsp; Hopefully the current situation will pass sooner rather than later and we can all go back to enjoying our sport.&nbsp; The most important thing is to stay safe and look after yourselves and your families and to keep up-to-date with current government advice.</div>
<div><br />Take care,</div>
<div>Brian Williams</div>
<div>Chairman</div>]]></description>
